creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132232936,imgsize-154276.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Japan, China clash in high-stakes maritime standoff near disputed islands]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132231419.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Japan's coast guard expelled Chinese vessels from waters near disputed islands. China stated its coast guard warned and expelled an intruding Japanese fishing boat. The confrontation occurred amid already strained ties between the two Asian powers. The Senkaku-Diaoyu islands remain a major flashpoint for decades. The East China Sea region is strategically important due to proximity to Taiwan.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/east-china-sea-tensions-flare-japan-china-clash-in-high-stakes-maritime-standoff-near-disputed-senkaku-islands/articleshow/132231419.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/east-china-sea-tensions-flare-japan-china-clash-in-high-stakes-maritime-standoff-near-disputed-senkaku-islands/articleshow/132231419.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-07T11:35:03+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132231928,imgsize-742295.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Watch: Typhoon Maysak breaks dam wall in China, kills 2 and forces thousands to evacuate]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132231644.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Typhoon Maysak caused severe flooding and two deaths in China's Guangxi region. Thousands of residents were evacuated after extensive rainfall and reservoir emergencies. A dam breach sent a massive torrent of water downstream, impacting villages. Rescue efforts utilized drones to deliver supplies and evacuate stranded individuals. Relief funding and supplies have been allocated to support affected provinces.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/watch-typhoon-maysak-breaks-dam-wall-in-china-kills-2-and-forces-thousands-to-evacuate/articleshow/132231644.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/watch-typhoon-maysak-breaks-dam-wall-in-china-kills-2-and-forces-thousands-to-evacuate/articleshow/132231644.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-07T11:36:01+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI News Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132231919,imgsize-168868.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Meet Paranthropus: The ancient human cousin that may have made the first stone tools 2.6 million years ago]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132231316.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/meet-paranthropus-the-ancient-human-cousin-that-may-have-made-the-first-stone-tools-2-6-million-years-ago/articleshow/132231316.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/meet-paranthropus-the-ancient-human-cousin-that-may-have-made-the-first-stone-tools-2-6-million-years-ago/articleshow/132231316.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-07T11:12:44+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132231377,imgsize-98723.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Cliff swallows abandoned the California town they once filled every spring, then people came together to rebuild their homes and welcomed them back with an annual festival]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132231088.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/cliff-swallows-abandoned-the-california-town-they-once-filled-every-spring-then-people-came-together-to-rebuild-their-homes-and-welcomed-them-back-with-an-annual-festival/articleshow/132231088.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/cliff-swallows-abandoned-the-california-town-they-once-filled-every-spring-then-people-came-together-to-rebuild-their-homes-and-welcomed-them-back-with-an-annual-festival/articleshow/132231088.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-07T11:04:15+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Science Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132231234,imgsize-1264918.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Nasa’s Hubble captures a spectacular cluster of 500,000 ancient stars to mark America's 250th anniversary]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132217269.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/nasas-hubble-captures-a-spectacular-cluster-of-500000-ancient-stars-to-mark-americas-250th-anniversary/articleshow/132217269.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/nasas-hubble-captures-a-spectacular-cluster-of-500000-ancient-stars-to-mark-americas-250th-anniversary/articleshow/132217269.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-06T23:00:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Science Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132217257,imgsize-2122269.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Ukraine launches 400+ drones at Moscow after deadly Russian strikes ahead of Nato summit]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132230065.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Ukraine launched over 400 drones at Moscow and struck Belgorod region. This offensive followed a deadly Russian missile and drone barrage across Ukraine. Ukrainian President Zelenskyy renewed his appeal for stronger Western air defense systems. He urged the United States to grant licenses for Patriot missile production. NATO leaders will discuss Ukraine's war and military assistance at their summit.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-launches-400-drones-at-moscow-after-deadly-russian-strikes-ahead-of-nato-summit/articleshow/132230065.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-launches-400-drones-at-moscow-after-deadly-russian-strikes-ahead-of-nato-summit/articleshow/132230065.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-07T10:08:13+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132230393,imgsize-33752.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[China sentences former official to death in $325 million bribery case]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132228523.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[The Changzhou Intermediate People's Court in Jiangsu province said Yang accepted the illicit payments between 1993 and 2023 in return for helping individuals and companies secure projects, business opportunities, land allocations and financial support. According to the court, the bribes were paid in exchange for assistance with "undertaking projects, business operations, land grants and working capital."]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-sentences-former-official-to-death-in-325-million-bribery-case/articleshow/132228523.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-sentences-former-official-to-death-in-325-million-bribery-case/articleshow/132228523.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-07T08:01:12+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132228749,imgsize-1238902.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[China test fires missile into Pacific, sparks alarm]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132228307.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-test-fires-missile-into-pacific-sparks-alarm/articleshow/132228307.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-test-fires-missile-into-pacific-sparks-alarm/articleshow/132228307.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-07T07:11:17+05:30</pubDate><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132228326,imgsize-3386681.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Oil tanker hit at Hormuz: US accuses Iran of attacking 2 commercial ships; mulls action]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132228226.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/oil-tanker-hit-at-hormuz-us-accuses-iran-of-attacking-2-commercial-ships-mulls-counter-strike/articleshow/132228226.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/oil-tanker-hit-at-hormuz-us-accuses-iran-of-attacking-2-commercial-ships-mulls-counter-strike/articleshow/132228226.cms]]></