</description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/therell-either-be-a-deal-with-iran-or-us-will-finish-the-job-donald-trump/articleshow/132228088.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/therell-either-be-a-deal-with-iran-or-us-will-finish-the-job-donald-trump/articleshow/132228088.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-07T06:33:01+05:30</pubDate><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132228122,imgsize-81138.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Clashes break out in Sri Lankan jail, 26 dead, over 100 hurt]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132228105.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/clashes-break-out-in-sri-lankan-jail-26-dead-over-100-hurt/articleshow/132228105.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/clashes-break-out-in-sri-lankan-jail-26-dead-over-100-hurt/articleshow/132228105.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-07T06:25:37+05:30</pubDate><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132228104,imgsize-493302.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[TTP claims killing of Pakistan Air Force officer in Islamabad]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132228000.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/ttp-claims-killing-of-pakistan-air-force-officer-in-islamabad/articleshow/132228000.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/ttp-claims-killing-of-pakistan-air-force-officer-in-islamabad/articleshow/132228000.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-07T06:12:56+05:30</pubDate><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132228060,imgsize-123844.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[“My prayers weren’t answered”: IShowSpeed abruptly bursts into tears after Spain eliminate Portugal from FIFA World Cup]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132227777.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[IShowSpeed was left heartbroken after Spain defeated Portugal 1-0 in the FIFA World Cup 2026 Round of 16. Mikel Merino scored in stoppage time to send Spain through and end Cristiano Ronaldo’s final World Cup campaign. Speed became emotional during his reaction, saying he believed Portugal would win the tournament before later thanking Ronaldo for everything.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/my-prayers-werent-answered-ishowspeed-abruptly-bursts-into-tears-after-spain-eliminate-portugal-from-fifa-world-cup/articleshow/132227777.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/my-prayers-werent-answered-ishowspeed-abruptly-bursts-into-tears-after-spain-eliminate-portugal-from-fifa-world-cup/articleshow/132227777.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-07T04:46:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132227772,imgsize-581750.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA["One more fight, Charlie": Candace Owens sends defiant message as Charlie Kirk family pleads for privacy at Tyler Robinson hearing]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132227845.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Tyler Robinson's preliminary hearing in the Charlie Kirk murder case began under heavy security, with the court deciding whether there is enough evidence for a trial. Charlie Kirk's widow Erika and his parents asked for privacy, calling the proceedings a painful reminder of their loss. Meanwhile, Candace Owens posted, "One more fight, Charlie. I don't fear these demons. We will win," taking a far more defiant public stance as the case continues.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/one-more-fight-charlie-candace-owens-sends-defiant-message-as-charlie-kirk-family-pleads-for-privacy-at-tyler-robinson-hearing/articleshow/132227845.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/one-more-fight-charlie-candace-owens-sends-defiant-message-as-charlie-kirk-family-pleads-for-privacy-at-tyler-robinson-hearing/articleshow/132227845.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-07T05:42:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132227845,imgsize-115490.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Finnish proverb of the day: "The forest answers in the same way one shouts at it" teaches us that we get what we do to others]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132225485.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/finnish-proverb-of-the-day-the-forest-answers-in-the-same-way-one-shouts-at-it-teaches-us-that-we-get-what-we-do-to-others/articleshow/132225485.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/finnish-proverb-of-the-day-the-forest-answers-in-the-same-way-one-shouts-at-it-teaches-us-that-we-get-what-we-do-to-others/articleshow/132225485.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-07T02:14:07+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132225489,imgsize-2867828.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Kick Streamer Raja Jackson jailed following Kick livestream attack on wrestler Syko Stu]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132225474.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Kick streamer Raja Jackson has begun a ninety-day jail sentence for assaulting wrestler Syko Stu.  The attack occurred during a live Kick broadcast in August of last year.  Jackson must also pay eighty-one thousand dollars in restitution to Syko Stu.  Syko Stu suffered severe injuries but has forgiven Jackson for the incident.  The streamer will also serve two years of formal probation following his release.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/kick-streamer-raja-jackson-jailed-following-kick-livestream-attack-on-wrestler-syko-stu/articleshow/132225474.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/kick-streamer-raja-jackson-jailed-following-kick-livestream-attack-on-wrestler-syko-stu/articleshow/132225474.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-07T01:58:57+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132225472,imgsize-442787.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Best proverb of the day: 'The ocean keeps every secret, but charges salt for storage']]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132225441.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[The ocean stands as a vast archive, modifying its essence with every new element it encounters. This mirrors the way human memory and organizational structures evolve through absorbed experiences. Current scientific findings reveal rising carbon dioxide levels are reshaping ocean chemistry, leading to acidification. Moreover, relentless plastic pollution has invaded even the most secluded oceanic depths. Similarly, digital records and unresolved disputes in workplaces exemplify transformation in our lives.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/etimes/trending/best-proverb-of-the-day-the-ocean-keeps-every-secret-but-charges-salt-for-storage-and-every-hidden-truth-returns-altered-by-time-and-chemistry/articleshow/132225441.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/etimes/trending/best-proverb-of-the-day-the-ocean-keeps-every-secret-but-charges-salt-for-storage-and-every-hidden-truth-returns-altered-by-time-and-chemistry/articleshow/132225441.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-07T01:55:57+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Trending Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132225465,imgsize-160684.cms"/></item></channel></rss>